Essential Sections of a Portfolio Website
Homepage (Introduction)

A short bio or tagline.
A high-quality image of yourself or a creative background.
About Me

A detailed description of your background, expertise, and interests.
Projects (Portfolio Section)

A showcase of your best projects with descriptions and links to live demos or GitHub repositories.
Skills & Expertise

A list of programming languages, frameworks, tools, and technologies you are proficient in.
Resume / Experience

A downloadable resume (PDF) and an overview of your work experience, internships, and education.
Contact Section

Email, social media links (LinkedIn, GitHub), and a contact form.
